From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kirill Kasaurov <kirill.kasaurov@amd.com>
Date: Tue, 6 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] [clang] Guard optional tool test deps with if(TARGET)

clang-linker-wrapper, clang-nvlink-wrapper, and clang-sycl-linker are
unconditionally listed in CLANG_TEST_DEPS but can be disabled via
CLANG_TOOL_<NAME>_BUILD=OFF, causing configure-time failures when
LLVM_INCLUDE_TESTS=ON.

Guard them with if(TARGET ...) following the existing pattern used for
lld and llvm-lto.

diff --git a/clang/test/CMakeLists.txt b/clang/test/CMakeLists.txt
index 1120870889d5..b1b13c2be379 100644
--- a/clang/test/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/clang/test/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -101,16 +101,19 @@ list(APPEND CLANG_TEST_DEPS
   clang-diff
   clang-installapi
   clang-scan-deps
-  clang-linker-wrapper
-  clang-nvlink-wrapper
   clang-offload-bundler
   clang-ssaf-linker
-  clang-sycl-linker
   diagtool
   hmaptool
   ssaf-format
   )
 
+foreach(_tool clang-linker-wrapper clang-nvlink-wrapper clang-sycl-linker)
+  if(TARGET ${_tool})
+    list(APPEND CLANG_TEST_DEPS ${_tool})
+  endif()
+endforeach()
+
 if(CLANG_ENABLE_CIR)
   list(APPEND CLANG_TEST_DEPS
     cir-opt
